prodNameC: 潘爾 登革熱IgG診斷試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.	Dengue Antigen (Serotypes 1,2,3,4) Coated Microwells –(12 x 8 wells ).
2.	Wash Buffer Concentrate : 20 x concentrate of phosphate buffered saline with Tween 20 and preservative 
3.	Serum Diluent : Tris buffeted saline with preservatives and additives.
4.	HRP Conjugated Anti-Human IgG : Horseradish peroxidase conjugated sheep anti-human IgG with preservative and protein stabilizers.
5.	Tetramethylbenzidine TMB :Amixture of 3,3’,5,5’-tetramethylbenzidine and hydrogen peroxide in a citrate-acid citrate buffer.
6.	Positive Control Serum : 200μL humanserum (contains 0.1% sodiumazide and 0.005% gentamycin sulphate).
7.	Cut-Off Calibrator Serum :  400μL humanserum (contains 0.1% sodiumazide and 0.005% gentamycin sulphate).
8.	Negative Control Serum : 200μL humanserum (contains 0.1% sodiumazide and 0.005% gentamycin sulphate).
9.	Stop Solution : 1M Phosphoric acid.
applicantAddr: 臺北市內湖區內湖路二段三九七號二樓
efficacy: 用於偵測革熱病毒IgG抗體(含1、2、3、4血清抗原)。
